rows.label: tlk43300241_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm just a nobody in the noble houses,
but I still got to travel a little bit with
my parents.

rows.label: tlk43300241_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Superbia's Divine Beast was starting to
deteriorate even back then.

rows.label: tlk43300241_02_msg0004
rows.name:
As is usual for Divine Beasts at the end of
their lifespan, the surface temperature
was rising, withering the plants...

rows.label: tlk43300241_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Nobody'd want to live
in a place like that.

rows.label: tlk43300241_02_msg0006
rows.name: Truly, Invidia's Divine Beast is the place to be.
